{"tid":1549573,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(有救啦)台灣義士係咪condom你有份話事","createTime":"2019-09-07T11:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T18:48:54.000Z","uid":263814,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8eca86b3027b5e49a52a5a341e6be87d94cf2288","tid":1549573,"uid":263814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開掛之達人成立左個基金專幫台灣流亡義士<br />\n你地唔係話手足唔係condom 點解咁少人捐㗎<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/香港勇武前線基金/?fbclid=IwAR1EuT0DdOv8_e2Wdf3lyiNOFaP50my49HcoLqGSctyTzkE9Kw9hZ5fupbQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1EuT0DdOv8_e2Wdf3lyiNOFaP50my49HcoLqGSctyTzkE9Kw9hZ5fupbQ&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=0ae80312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/香港勇武前線基金/?fbclid=IwAR1EuT0DdOv8_e2Wdf3lyiNOFaP50my49HcoLqGSctyTzkE9Kw9hZ5fupbQ</a><br />\n<br />\n「緊急籌款助義士」香港勇武前線基金正式成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n基金成立目的是為了因7月1日沖擊立法會而流亡台灣的義士，讓他們食得飽、著得暖。有義士聯絡我們聲稱直到現在仍沒有收到任何台灣機構的支援，而我們已經找到了一部份流亡在海外的義士。我們開掛團隊相信未來將會找到更多流亡在海外的義士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n而基金剩餘的部份會資助前線勇者，大部份勇者都因長期在前線而失去了工作、食不果腹，逹人的團隊和其他團隊很多也和家人決裂，甚至連住宿的地方也沒有。一號機原本的積蓄是夠兩年的生活，但也因為這兩個多月來為予資助前線購買裝備，生活費只剩下若三個月左右。如沒有勇者以死相博抗爭，條例一早就已經通過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n而前線勇者如果都被捕或因生存問題被迫放棄抗爭，黎緊這幾年,全香港的人將會全面被政府秋後算帳，無人幸免。因此，我們必須要讓前線隊友無後顧之憂，因此大家要全力支援我們! 萬分感激<br />\n <br />\n對於能否公開我同我隊員既真人比你地, 很抱歉, 如果我們公開左自己既身份，我地保證一早就會全軍覆沒<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小妹第一次開post 請多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d458b20efb4f2a5751e5b6170c8878b87a67472","tid":1549573,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd0151561f98286b114c6478917a73a9ecf244e","tid":1549573,"uid":263814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"聽日美領見"},{"pid":"eb52108469bed38693e221b58cd3236104018f3c","tid":1549573,"uid":263814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:08:42.000Z","msg":"美領有不反對 到時見"},{"pid":"efebe860a1189632e75841bf25ca826359ddd131","tid":1549573,"uid":194556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"學生幫推"},{"pid":"07ee7f90e617768050938f5cf5c074b3d493979d","tid":1549573,"uid":263814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:10:12.000Z","msg":"大家有力出力 有錢出錢"},{"pid":"8ca76c9eb781dd1b0bd36762c97ca718f4603c73","tid":1549573,"uid":263814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足 快啲入嚟"},{"pid":"956c894eca4181138e5c870e03291a68a2581656","tid":1549573,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f0dc79232e5120085e4570c8548634828cce3e","tid":1549573,"uid":263814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"聽日美領見"},{"pid":"29f7eae26ce504243d9ca1ecf9ec9e328a01fa71","tid":1549573,"uid":263814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"聽日美領見"},{"pid":"187a1e2886ebb0b4beb1ccb89333dd921a13084c","tid":1549573,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"樓豬係真開掛團隊?"},{"pid":"84fabb4d4ff50cda0e6d11a8d57c3195158f5fb9","tid":1549573,"uid":263814,"like":0